sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Local API client
    participant API as FastAPI route
    participant Loader as Demo inventory loader
    participant Models as Pydantic models
    participant Risk as Risk engine

    Client->>API: GET /risk-report
    API->>Loader: load_demo_inventory()
    Loader->>Models: validate fixture and relationships
    Models-->>Loader: Inventory
    Loader-->>API: Validated synthetic inventory
    API->>Risk: build_risk_report(inventory, as_of)
    Risk-->>API: RiskReport
    API-->>Client: JSON response
